{"tid":2008757,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"講下咩叫Blockchain區塊鏈技術","createTime":"2020-05-09T09:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T14:09:05.000Z","uid":149978,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"56b3a578fe44c31c84d3df08926b5599d6565700","tid":2008757,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:18:20.000Z","msg":"簡單來說，blockchain不是bitcoin，但bitcoin 係第一個成功採用 了blockchain 技術而創立的電子貨幣，無需以政府和實物背書，都可以升到一萬美元一牧。Bitcoin 令blockchain發揚光大，讓世界見識到blockchain的厲害。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>咩叫blockchain ?</strong><br />\nBlockchain係一個去中央化，採用點到點技術，高強度加密，程式碼完全open source的數據庫。Blockchain可以做到資料無法刪改，連Main developer和top admin都無法刪改。<br />\n<br />\n現在blockchain己經做到應用上不限於加密貨幣，還在商業和物流上都可以應用到，最主要係可以防hack和防惡意刪改。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>先睇睇傳統database係咁：</strong><br />\nTransaction id, from id, to id, amount<br />\n1,50,70, 120<br />\n2,90,80, 330<br />\n3,80,77,550<br />\n<br />\n<strong>再睇睇Blockchain的database係咁：</strong><br />\nTransaction id, from id, to id, amount, hash<br />\n1,50,70, 120,sha256(1,50,70,120)<br />\n2,90,80, 330,sha256(record 1 hash result + (2,00,80,330))<br />\n3,80,77,550,sha256(record 2 hash result + (<strong>3,80,77,550</strong>))<br />\n<br />\n<strong>咩叫sha256 hash：</strong><br />\n你當係一個checksum,類似身份證的括號數字，但身份證checksum複雜度只有1個數字，而sha256的複雜度係10^77個，即係用晒全球所有電腦的計算能力再花十萬年都破解唔到一條record。<br />\n<br />\n如果你改左任何一條record，個hash result就會broken，不過當然你可以重新計算晒所有hash再寫來去，然後改晒所有hash record，但極費時和極易被發現。<br />\n<br />\n另外， blockchain 係用peer to peer decentralize database，一條record會發送俾所有server，例如有十萬部server，除非你一次過改晒所有server record，或者至少改左百分之五十的server先得，否則無法改data。另外一些server持有人可能會定期print最後record個hash出黎，就算比你刪改到data，在blockchain技術下，data被改的事實都會被人通晒天，top admin and main developer無法用神不知鬼不覺形式改data。<br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n1) Certified blockchain expert, blockchain council<br />\n2) Professional certificate in blockchain for business, mooc edx with linux foundation course<br />\n3) Bachelor degree in computing<br />\n4) over 5 years practical work experience in IT"},{"pid":"3a6972b6e65ca044bbfc06de6d94f69f7e52cde1","tid":2008757,"uid":179837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:23:20.000Z","msg":"想自學it點入門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fc758bba85f06f782d75f6168b7a647af7d58e","tid":2008757,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a6972b6e65ca044bbfc06de6d94f69f7e52cde1","tid":2008757,"uid":179837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:23:20.000Z","msg":"想自學it點入門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:31:12.000Z","msg":"上網搵online course<br />\n去黃金商場買書<br />\n去圖書館借書<br />\n俾錢去電腦教學中心上堂<br />\n大學讀IT degree<br />\n<br />\n五大方法皆可"},{"pid":"c587dbfc87c247ecaf7bbac2aebbb87bcc997dd8","tid":2008757,"uid":179837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"20fc758bba85f06f782d75f6168b7a647af7d58e","tid":2008757,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a6972b6e65ca044bbfc06de6d94f69f7e52cde1","tid":2008757,"uid":179837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:23:20.000Z","msg":"想自學it點入門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:31:12.000Z","msg":"上網搵online course<br />\n去黃金商場買書<br />\n去圖書館借書<br />\n俾錢去電腦教學中心上堂<br />\n大學讀IT degree<br />\n<br />\n五大方法皆可"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:35:58.000Z","msg":"茫茫it海有咩入門topic<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a5868f6beae5d34616ceae01b826647f612714","tid":2008757,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a6972b6e65ca044bbfc06de6d94f69f7e52cde1","tid":2008757,"uid":179837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:23:20.000Z","msg":"想自學it點入門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:36:53.000Z","msg":"唔好入門<br />\n<br />\n自學個d